WEBVTT

00:08.458 --> 00:10.458
[lively music]

00:31.916 --> 00:33.916
[lively music continues]

01:18.083 --> 01:19.083
[yelps]

01:19.875 --> 01:21.875
[laughing]

01:24.875 --> 01:26.291
Yes, go!

01:26.375 --> 01:28.833
And... and tell your gangster father,

01:29.041 --> 01:31.333
that if he's going to pay her school fees,

01:31.416 --> 01:33.125
he should get her a new uniform.

01:33.208 --> 01:34.125
[laughs]

01:34.208 --> 01:35.833
[student 1] Let's go, guys!

01:37.875 --> 01:40.583
[upbeat music]

01:43.250 --> 01:45.250
[no audible dialogue]

01:48.416 --> 01:49.625
-[thumps]
-[shrieks]

01:50.625 --> 01:53.125
[indistinct clamoring]

01:54.416 --> 01:56.833
[screaming]

01:56.916 --> 01:59.166
[indistinct chatter]

02:03.333 --> 02:05.333
[chuckles]

02:07.791 --> 02:08.625
[giggles]

02:10.458 --> 02:11.458
[clicks tongue, grunts]

02:14.291 --> 02:15.208
[sighs]

02:18.250 --> 02:20.250
[Chike's father]
<i>So you now fighting like common touts?</i>

02:20.375 --> 02:22.458
Hm? Is that what you want to be, Chike?

02:23.458 --> 02:25.041
Is that how I'm raising you up?

02:25.250 --> 02:28.083
I'm talking to you! Talk to me! Huh?

02:31.166 --> 02:32.208
[goons speaking indistinctly]

02:32.291 --> 02:33.416
[goon in Hausa]
Your father!

02:33.500 --> 02:34.875
-[goon 1] Hey!
-[gunshot]

02:37.916 --> 02:39.708
-[Chike's father] Okay.
-[cocks gun]

02:40.666 --> 02:41.750
-Come here!
-[goon 2] Hey! Hey!

02:41.833 --> 02:43.958
-[gunshots]
-[goons groaning]

02:45.375 --> 02:46.291
[goon yells]

02:48.250 --> 02:51.041
-[goon grunts, groans]
-[thwacking]

02:53.375 --> 02:54.791
-[thumps]
-[goon groans]

02:55.625 --> 02:56.708
[gunshot]

02:57.541 --> 02:59.625
[somber music]

03:08.625 --> 03:10.625
[sighs deeply]

03:25.625 --> 03:27.958
[blows air]

03:36.750 --> 03:39.416
[pimp] Before the end of the year,
the kind of money she will make for you...

03:39.500 --> 03:41.125
-you will just go and collect a title.
-Mm-hm.

03:41.208 --> 03:42.375
[speaks Igbo]

03:42.458 --> 03:43.750
[both laugh]

03:43.833 --> 03:46.166
[in Igbo]
They will sing your praises!

03:46.250 --> 03:49.333
-They will hail you!
-[Chike] Chief!

03:49.416 --> 03:50.708
[both laughing]

03:50.791 --> 03:52.416
[in English]
You haven't yet sold your daughter

03:52.500 --> 03:53.541
into prostitution.

03:54.208 --> 03:57.166
How dare you come into my house
and talk to me like this!

03:57.250 --> 03:58.958
Eh? Will you get out!

03:59.041 --> 04:00.333
[in Igbo]
Please take it easy.

04:00.416 --> 04:02.333
-Who... who is this girl?
-Let it go.

04:02.416 --> 04:03.833
[in English]
How do you sleep at night?

04:04.000 --> 04:05.125
Chike.

04:05.750 --> 04:07.666
[chuckles]
[pimp] Tell me, huh?

04:08.458 --> 04:12.166
How many people did your father kill,
before the police caught up with him?

04:12.333 --> 04:13.291
Oh?

04:13.708 --> 04:16.333
Ten? Eleven?
[scoffs]

04:16.416 --> 04:17.500
How did he sleep at night?

04:17.583 --> 04:19.791
At least he didn't make his money
on the backs of young girls.

04:19.875 --> 04:24.291
What I do provides a source of income
for these people.

04:24.375 --> 04:25.333
Mm-hm.

04:26.125 --> 04:30.083
God does not come down to bless you,
he sends people.

04:30.375 --> 04:32.208
[pimp] I am godsent to them.

04:32.500 --> 04:34.041
What I do makes me a hero!

04:34.125 --> 04:37.541
Huh? And as for her, a better life.

04:37.625 --> 04:38.750
For him...

04:39.333 --> 04:40.333
more money.

04:40.416 --> 04:42.791
[laughs]

04:43.291 --> 04:47.333
[stutters]
Look, this does not concern you.

04:47.416 --> 04:48.291
[snickers]

04:48.375 --> 04:51.958
Grace knows her obligation
to, to her family.

04:52.041 --> 04:53.083
[thuds]

04:53.166 --> 04:55.625
There's a million naira.
Fuck your obligation!

04:55.708 --> 04:56.833
[pimp] I like that.

04:56.916 --> 04:58.375
You got that fire.

04:58.458 --> 04:59.875
Now we are doing business.

04:59.958 --> 05:02.416
[in Igbo]
You are doing the dance that's for elders.

05:06.083 --> 05:08.791
Wait, wait, wait.

05:08.875 --> 05:10.625
[in English]
Wait. Huh?

05:10.708 --> 05:11.958
Leave this aside.

05:12.041 --> 05:13.041
[in Igbo]
Take it easy.

05:13.125 --> 05:15.916
[in English]
I increase the offer to two million naira.

05:16.541 --> 05:17.541
[Grace's mother] No!

05:19.291 --> 05:20.541
[Grace's father] No, what?

05:21.250 --> 05:22.458
I said no.

05:22.541 --> 05:23.791
[Grace's father] No, what?

05:24.125 --> 05:26.791
You will accept the one million naira
from Chike.

05:28.083 --> 05:30.541
Take Grace. Go. Never come back.

05:30.625 --> 05:32.791
Are you crazy?
He is offering us two million.

05:32.875 --> 05:34.166
-[glass clinks]
-What is that?

05:34.250 --> 05:35.833
You're trying to spoil business
for us here,

05:35.916 --> 05:37.708
do you know how much we are suffering
in this house?

05:38.708 --> 05:40.750
[gloomy music]

05:43.333 --> 05:46.000
Chike, where did you get
a million naira from?

05:46.500 --> 05:48.000
I sold my left kidney.

05:48.083 --> 05:49.750
-Oh, be serious.
-[chuckles]

05:51.000 --> 05:52.500
I got it from Saliu.

05:53.375 --> 05:55.083
Saliu the drug dealer?

05:55.791 --> 05:56.958
Why would he want...

05:58.708 --> 06:00.333
Chike, what would you have to do?

06:00.958 --> 06:02.291
Free trips to Malaysia.

06:02.375 --> 06:04.125
-[gasps]
-What?

06:04.208 --> 06:07.000
All they need to do
is catch you after one trip

06:07.083 --> 06:08.333
and you're dead, Malaysia.

06:08.416 --> 06:10.416
Then I have to make sure
they don't catch me, don't I?

06:11.333 --> 06:12.250
[sighs]

06:12.666 --> 06:13.708
What?

06:15.208 --> 06:16.875
-You are so awkward.
-[Grace] Thank you.

06:16.958 --> 06:18.125
Thank you.

06:21.291 --> 06:22.291
Let's go.

06:24.208 --> 06:25.291
Where are we going?

06:25.375 --> 06:27.583
[blows raspberry]
Somewhere far from here.

06:31.000 --> 06:32.833
Any small thing you will be crying.

06:32.916 --> 06:33.875
[giggles]

06:41.833 --> 06:43.875
Saliu called while you were in the shower.

06:43.958 --> 06:45.208
[Chike] What did he want?

06:45.583 --> 06:48.666
He said you're going to Hong Kong
and the ticket is in the hotel room.

06:48.750 --> 06:49.916
Fine, whatever.

06:50.000 --> 06:50.875
[clears throat]

06:50.958 --> 06:52.208
How do I look?

06:52.291 --> 06:54.041
[both laugh]

06:54.125 --> 06:56.875
You look so good
and almost getting ready to convert.

06:56.958 --> 06:58.125
Thank you.

07:03.791 --> 07:04.625
Grace.

07:05.541 --> 07:07.125
You are still paying her.

07:07.208 --> 07:09.083
She is my mother. I'm sending her money.

07:09.166 --> 07:11.000
She was going to sell you
into sex slavery.

07:11.083 --> 07:12.291
You don't owe her anything.

07:12.375 --> 07:14.000
It's not your business.

07:14.458 --> 07:15.375
[knocks on door]

07:16.208 --> 07:17.500
Are you expecting somebody?

07:21.041 --> 07:23.250
[tense music]

07:30.375 --> 07:31.458
[Chike] Who are you?

07:32.583 --> 07:34.791
Pack your things, you don't have time.

07:38.875 --> 07:39.916
[door closes]

07:42.250 --> 07:45.416
Do you know it takes an average male
three trips before they are busted

07:45.500 --> 07:47.458
and you have done what? 10, 15?

07:47.833 --> 07:49.125
I think you should leave.

07:49.208 --> 07:52.583
Saliu has just been arrested by NDLEA
and he's given you up.

07:53.041 --> 07:55.666
[Madame] Ah, Saliu is quite the drug lord.

07:55.750 --> 07:59.625
Cross-continental mix.
Malaysia, Russia, Mexico.

07:59.708 --> 08:02.458
It was quite a queue to capture him.

08:03.583 --> 08:04.750
But you two...

08:05.416 --> 08:07.041
Apparently, you're not just couriers,

08:07.125 --> 08:10.166
you also trained other couriers
from different countries.

08:10.250 --> 08:11.833
Just to hear him tell it.

08:12.291 --> 08:15.625
You were major players
in the drug network, and you...

08:16.166 --> 08:18.583
were meeting up with drug lords
in several countries.

08:18.666 --> 08:19.666
Information you hold...

08:19.750 --> 08:21.500
Wait, why are you telling us this?

08:23.291 --> 08:24.541
So how did you do it?

08:24.791 --> 08:26.083
How did you avoid being caught?

08:26.166 --> 08:28.875
[Chike] And how do we know you're
not trying to trick us into confessing?

08:28.958 --> 08:30.125
-I don't...
-[Grace] Chike.

08:30.875 --> 08:32.000
What difference does it make?

08:32.541 --> 08:35.083
Twenty trips, we did 20 trips.

08:35.541 --> 08:36.916
We made friends on social media

08:37.000 --> 08:39.000
and joined missions
with Malaysian connections.

08:39.833 --> 08:42.125
We had reason each time,
that's how we did it.

08:42.458 --> 08:43.500
Mm.

08:46.458 --> 08:49.083
[suspenseful music]

08:49.625 --> 08:51.625
Call the number on this card
when you're done.

08:56.916 --> 08:58.958
Go, go, go...

09:08.125 --> 09:10.416
[suspenseful music]

09:17.708 --> 09:18.750
-Grace!
-Yes?

09:18.833 --> 09:19.666
Let's go!

09:24.000 --> 09:26.291
[tense music]

09:32.583 --> 09:33.875
[knocking on door]

09:39.041 --> 09:41.208
[foreboding music]

09:55.875 --> 09:57.958
[ominous music]

10:10.666 --> 10:12.708
[suspenseful music]

10:24.500 --> 10:25.833
[sighs]

10:38.666 --> 10:40.708
[light music]

10:46.000 --> 10:49.250
[inaudible singing]

10:53.625 --> 10:55.666
[light music]

11:07.291 --> 11:09.583
[light music continues]

11:26.583 --> 11:28.541
[Chike] Uh, what is this place?

11:29.083 --> 11:30.750
[Madame] A private members club.

11:33.541 --> 11:35.291
-[Chike] You run a whore house.
-[Madame sighs]

11:36.875 --> 11:38.166
Call the police.

11:38.250 --> 11:39.916
I'd rather go to jail than do that.

11:40.000 --> 11:41.666
I do not run a whore house.

11:50.041 --> 11:50.875
[clicks tongue]

11:51.833 --> 11:53.833
-[sighs]
-What do you want from us?

11:58.416 --> 12:02.291
<i>♪ Smothered by the hands of the one ♪</i>

12:02.375 --> 12:06.291
<i>♪ Who should have loved me
With the love of the one ♪</i>

12:06.375 --> 12:08.291
<i>♪ Into your arms we fell ♪</i>

12:08.375 --> 12:11.958
<i>♪ We never had a say ♪</i>

12:14.500 --> 12:18.583
<i>♪ They said we were the beautiful ones ♪</i>

12:18.666 --> 12:21.333
<i>♪ Born before our time ♪</i>

12:21.416 --> 12:24.166
<i>♪ So we put our makeup on ♪</i>

12:24.250 --> 12:28.750
<i>♪ To hide away our flaws ♪</i>

12:30.291 --> 12:33.125
<i>♪ The struggle is in vain ♪</i>

12:33.208 --> 12:37.750
<i>♪ We have succumbed to your embrace ♪</i>

12:38.500 --> 12:44.625
<i>♪ Hands up in the air we surrender ♪</i>

12:45.916 --> 12:49.000
<i>♪ When the lights go out ♪</i>

12:49.083 --> 12:50.958
<i>♪ Who will be there? ♪</i>

12:51.041 --> 12:53.958
<i>♪ Who will be there for us? ♪</i>

12:54.041 --> 12:56.916
<i>♪ When the lights go out ♪</i>

