-How come?

1:34:36.708 --> 1:34:37.708
[Bamidele] How?

1:34:42.666 --> 1:34:44.791
I cannot believe she didn't tell me.

1:34:45.625 --> 1:34:46.625
How?

1:34:47.000 --> 1:34:48.791
Why would I wanna fake my own death?

1:34:48.875 --> 1:34:50.750
Because you don't want Madame
to steal your company.

1:34:50.833 --> 1:34:54.166
Come on, Aunty Enitan will never do that,
we have a deal.

1:34:54.791 --> 1:34:57.125
