like she did me?

1:34:58.416 --> 1:35:01.083
Hey, if I'm wrong,
you don't have to do anything.

1:35:01.458 --> 1:35:04.291
I go to jail and you're happily at home
for your family's crimes.

1:35:04.375 --> 1:35:05.708
But if I'm right,

1:35:05.791 --> 1:35:07.333
how do you get your company back?

1:35:08.333 --> 1:35:12.125
You are a horrible, manipulative person.

1:35:12.208 --> 1:35:14.166
Yeah, I learned from the best.

1:35:14.708 --> 1:35:16.000
And so did you.

1:35:16.083 --> 1:35:19.125
-I'm nothing like you.
-[Chike] Yeah, yeah.

1:35:19.208 --> 1:35:20.416
My father was an assassin,

1:35:20.500 --> 1:35:22.250
my mother was a whore,
and I was a drug trafficker.

1:35:22.833 --> 1:35:24.583
And the surface were nothing alike,

1:35:24.666 --> 1:35:27.291
-but Madame found--
-I am nothing like you.

1:35:27.375 --> 1:35:28.333
Motunrayo.

1:35:29.166 --> 1:35:32.000
You are about to set up your brother
for a crime he didn't commit,

1:35:32.083 --> 1:35:33.583
and use that to blackmail your mother

1:35:33.666 --> 1:35:35.791
into handing over
a large share of her company

1:35:36.166 --> 1:35:38.000
to her husband's mistress.

1:35:38.083 --> 1:35:39.125
Yeah.

1:35:39.333 --> 1:35:40.708
You are nothing like me.

1:35:43.041 --> 1:35:45.208
